---
title: Chicken and Cannellini Bean Cassoulet with Greek style cheese and fluffy rice
description: This savoury tomato-y stew is a guaranteed weeknight winner. The perfectly fluffy rice is perfect for soaking up every last drop of this rich, hearty bean and chicken dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R03_W01_IE_IECFQP0165-2_Main_high-f98d62e3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/chicken-and-cannellini-bean-cassoulet-638f17572d630dceaa85ac74-14bd4ee4.pdf
